Whelp This Has Been A Fun Project. Buying And Gut Renovating During The Pandemic Was One Of The Most Financially & Emotionally Challenging Projects For Us. It Was Super Arduous And We Felt Beyond Helpless And Frustrated During Most Of It. Add Three Kids, Relocating From The West Coast, Failed Rounds Of IVF And Quarantine On Top Of It All…..(our bathroom was sometimes our backyard 🙄) Let’s Just Say I Cried A Lot. 
So Proud Of Bringing This Home To It’s Glory…Still More To Do, But We Definitely Came A Long Way From When We Purchased It. 
My Husband And I Love Collaborating On Creative Projects Together. We Share A Similar Vision And It Strengthens Our Bond - Definitely Looking Forward To Our Next Endeavor Together. @harveynh 💕💕💕

social_posts.post_text:
Taking Control Of My Health And Being My Biggest Advocate Has Always Been Important To Me, But I Have Been Increasingly Frustrated For Many Years In Seeing That Health Insurance Companies And Docs Wouldn’t Recognize Me In The System Unless I Was Already Sick. Unfortunately The American Healthcare System Is Riddled With Inefficiencies, High Costs And So Much Red Tape Making It Impossible To Navigate. 
I Am So Happy The @prenuvo Full-Body MRI Scan Has Come To Market To Help With Early Detection Which Is What We All Deserve. I Realize For Some, This Information Can Be Scary, But It Allows Us To Respond To Our Health-care Needs Instead Of Having To React. 
It Is Not Lost On Me That @prenuvo Comes At A Premium Cost, But My Hope Is That Through Awareness They Can Build Up Enough Demand To Drive The Prices Down And Hopefully Enough Recognition To Get Health Insurance Companies To Cover. They Were Kind Enough To Offer $300 Off For My Followers Using This code: PROMO CODE: JENNE (PRENUVO.COM/JENNE).
It Takes About 15 Business Days To Receive My Results - Will Keep You Posted On This Process.
